OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FA grandfather had lifesaving surgery -
OL,7,Fin a medical first - after being
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with severe heart failure
OL,9,Fwith just days to live.
OL,11,FUnusually, the damage to his Patrick
OL,12,FMulholland's heart had been caused by
OL,13,Fa tumour elsewhere in his body that
OL,14,Fwas releasing a chemical into his
OL,15,Fblood.
OL,17,FThe 67-year old, from Jarrow, on South
OL,18,FTyneside, had been suffering from
OL,19,Fstomach and bowel symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
