OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FMr Mulholland required complex heart
OL,7,Fsurgery which saw all four of his
OL,8,Fvalves replaced at once.
OL,10,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees he did not
OL,11,Finitially take in the diagnosis.
OL,13,F"I didn't think it was that bad, you
OL,14,Fknow what I mean?" he said, "but now I
OL,15,Flook back on it, it's massive.
OL,17,F"A couple of people said I wouldn't
OL,18,Fcome out of intensive care, I was that
OL,19,Fbad, you know."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
