OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FMr Mulholland's diagnosis was
OL,7,Fextremely rare.
OL,9,FThe tumour in his bowel was releasing
OL,10,Fa chemical into the bloodstream that
OL,11,Fwas attacking his heart, resulting in
OL,12,Fsevere damage to all four heart
OL,13,Fvalves, which work to ensure that
OL,14,Fblood flows in the right direction.
OL,16,FIt is unusual for a tumour of this
OL,17,Fkind to damage heart valves, and when
OL,18,Fit does, it generally affects just one.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
