OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FGiven the threat to Mr Mulholland's
OL,7,Flife, the surgical team was forced to
OL,8,Fremove all four of his heart valves,
OL,9,Freplacing them with functioning
OL,10,Falternatives.
OL,12,FThe procedure was carried out by team
OL,13,Fat Newcastle's Freeman Hospital led by
OL,14,FProfessor Stephen Clark, who describes
OL,15,Fthis situation as "unique".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
