OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FThe heart surgeon explained: "The
OL,7,Fsurgery itself took around five hours
OL,8,Fto perform and Mr Mulholland's heart
OL,9,Fhad to be stopped for about three
OL,10,Fhours for us to replace all four of
OL,11,Fthose heart valves.
OL,13,FProf Clark continued: "Only eleven of
OL,14,Fthese operations have been performed
OL,15,Fin the United Kingdom through history
OL,16,Fand we're fortunate enough to have
OL,17,Fdone four of these operations here in
OL,18,FNewcastle."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
