OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FThis rare situation was made all the
OL,7,Fmore noteworthy as Professor Clark
OL,8,Fused a new generation of specialist
OL,9,Fvalve, which is designed to be more
OL,10,Fdurable.
OL,12,FAccording to Newcastle Hospitals, Mr
OL,13,FMulholland is the first patient in the
OL,14,Fworld to receive the new devices in a
OL,15,Fquadruple replacement.
OL,17,FIn view of the circumstances, pictures
OL,18,Fof the procedure were filmed by the
OL,19,FNewcastle team, as a training tool for
OL,20,Fcolleagues around the world.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
