OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FBack home in Jarrow, Mr Mulholland is
OL,7,Fcontinuing his recovery from the heart
OL,8,Fsurgery with support from his family.
OL,10,FAs someone who was used to walking and
OL,11,Fcycling, it is a long - and sometimes
OL,12,Ffrustrating - journey.JHe said: "Not
OL,13,Fthat I'm bad bad, but it's not what
OL,14,FI'm used to.
OL,16,F"But I'm here, progressing, and
OL,17,Fhopefully the cancer treatment goes
OL,18,Fwell."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
