OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FWhile his four new heart valves are
OL,7,Fdesigned to withstand many years of
OL,8,Fuse, they also bring another benefit.
OL,10,FThey are designed to be replaced, if
OL,11,Frequired, through a minimally invasive
OL,12,Fprocedure, rather than further open
OL,13,Fheart surgery.
OL,15,FProf Clark explained: "They are
OL,16,Fdesigned to be very durable and can be
OL,17,Freplaced if they wear out over the
OL,18,Fyears without more surgery, by placing
OL,19,Ffolded up valves through an artery in
OL,20,Fthe groin."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
