OL,3,CGrandfather in 'world first' heart op
OL,4,Cafter being given days to live
OL,6,FFor now, Mr Mulholland is embarking on
OL,7,Fa course of radiotherapy to tackle his
OL,8,Fabdominal tumour, in what is hopefully
OL,9,Fanother step towards returning to
OL,10,Fhealth.
